CatDescriptText: The flyer Tom Twiss is holding reads, " Stop State Police Now !!!, mass rally thursday 8pm, Bethesda U.P. Church, 7220 Bennett St., Hear The Parent's Side, Hear The Victims Side, Hear The Truth! (see reverse side), Citizens Opposed to a Police State (COPS)".  Some of the literature on the shelf in background reads, "Revolutionary Strategy in the 1973 Argentine Elections", "Political Rights Defense Fund" and "The Structure and Organizational Principles of the Party".
TitMainTitle: Tom Twiss, student at University of Pittsburgh, holding sign that reads, "Stop Police State Now! Mass rally Thursday 8 pm, Bethesda U.P. Church, 7020 Bennett Street", with revolutionary literature on shelf in background
